verbose_text: We have noticed a recent study that reported that CSE induced expression of TLR4 and LPS binding in another epithelial cell line, namely 16-HBE [XREF_BIBR], and thus it is tempting to speculate that this could be one possible explanation for the observed synergy between the CSE and LPS treatment of NCI-H292 cells and the transcription of MUC7 and MUC5AC.
